## Prescription Components

### Section Header Pattern
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Consistent section headers
.prescription-section {
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
  }
}
```

### List Item Pattern
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Prescription/exercise list items
.prescription-list,
.exercise-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  
  .prescription-item,
  .exercise-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 8px;
    
    .prescription-content,
    .exercise-content {
      flex: 1;
      
      .prescription-name,
      .exercise-name {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      
      .prescription-detail {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
    }
    
    .prescription-actions,
    .exercise-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }
  }
}
```

### Card Grid Pattern
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Cognitive training cards
.cognitive-cards-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
  
  .cognitive-card {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    
    .cognitive-card-content {
      .cognitive-card-name {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .cognitive-card-difficulty {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
    
    .cognitive-card-actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
  }
}
```

### Add Card Pattern
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Dashed border add card
.cognitive-card.add-card,
.cognitive-card-add {
  background: #fafafa;
  border: 2px dashed #d9d9d9;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  min-height: 100px;
  
  .add-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  
  span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
  }
  
  &:hover {
    border-color: #1890ff;
    background: #f0f5ff;
    
    .add-icon,
    span {
      color: #1890ff;
    }
  }
}
```

