```

### Icon + Text Actions
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Action items with icons
.action-items {
  display: flex;
  gap: 4px;
  
  .action-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #336fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    
    span {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    
    &:hover {
      background: #f0f5ff;
      border-color: #d6e4ff;
    }
  }
}
```

