## Naming Conventions

### BEM-like Structure
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Component > Element > Modifier
.component-name {
  .component-element {
    .element-detail {
      // styles
    }
    
    &.modifier {
      // modified styles
    }
  }
}

// ❌ BAD - Flat structure
.component-name { }
.component-element { }
.element-detail { }
```

### Semantic Class Names
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Descriptive names
.user-info-container
.prescription-list
.action-items
.status-badge

// ❌ BAD - Generic names
